-- Fiat Favors Peugeot for Commercial Vehicle Alliance, MF Reports
-- B y   E l i s a   M a r t i n u z z i
-- 2012-03-10T11:51:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-10/fiat-favors-peugeot-for-commercial-vehicle-alliance-mf-reports.html
Fiat SpA (F)  favors an alliance with
PSA Peugeot Citroen for the production of commercial vehicles,
 Milano Finanza  reported, citing an unidentified person close to
the Italian carmaker.  Fiat is considering a deal with Peugeot for light-
commercial vehicles and an option may be to expand the
operations in  Turkey , the Milan-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisa Martinuzzi in Milan at 
 emartinuzzi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Edward Evans at 
 eevans3@bloomberg.net  